revision.text:
{{one source|date=June 2017}}
See [[Arsinoe (Northwest Cyprus)]], as this location was confused by Strabo with the true location. See T⊘nnes Bekker‐Nielsen (1999): Strabo and Ptolemy on the geography of western cyprus, Symbolae Osloenses: Norwegian Journal of Greek and Latin Studies, 74:1, 151-162, DOI: 10.1080/00397679908590960 <ref>https://www.academia.edu/951882/Strabo_and_Ptolemy_on_the_Geography_of_Western_Cyprus</ref>

