==Landmarks== La Rousse is a [[residential community]]. [[Tour Odéon]], a [[mixed-use development]], is located on ''Avenue de l'Annonciade''. At 170 m, Tour Odéon is the tallest structure in Monaco.
==Notable residents== *[[Chris Froome]]; English cyclist
